{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"알고리즘 - 문자열 다루기 기본","date":"2020-01-09","slug":"2020-01-09-algorithm-11","content":"<h4>문제설명</h4>\n<p>문자열 s의 길이가 4 혹은 6이고, 숫자로만 구성돼있는지 확인해주는 함수, solution을 완성하세요. 예를 들어 s가 a234이면 False를 리턴하고 1234라면 True를 리턴하면 됩니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>s는 길이 1 이상, 길이 8 이하인 문자열입니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h4>입출력 예</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>s</th>\n<th>return</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\"a234\"</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\"1234\"</td>\n<td>true</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>풀이</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">solution</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">phone_number</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">let</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">answer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">answer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">parseInt</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">&#x26;&#x26;</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">length</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">4</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">||</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">length</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">6</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">?</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">true</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">:</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">false</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li><code>parseInt</code>메소드를 사용해 문자열을 숫자로 바꿀 때 원래 매개변수랑 같고,<br>\n문자열의 길이가 4, 6이면 값을 반환해준다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>다른 사람 풀이 01</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">alpha_string46</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">var</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">regex</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\"> /</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">^</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\\d</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">{6}</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">|</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">^</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\\d</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">{4}</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">$</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">/</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">regex</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">test</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>정규식을 사용하여 반환한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>다른 사람 풀이 02</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">alpha_string46</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">length</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">4</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">||</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">length</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">6</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">?</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">!</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">isNaN</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">:</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">false</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>매개변수의 길이가 4, 6이면 <code>isNaN</code> 메소드를 사용하여 값을 반환한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>배운점</strong></h4>\n<p>일단 1번 풀이는 정규식이라 넘기고, 2번 풀이는 내가 중간 과정에 했던 풀이다.<br>\n다른 사람 풀이에 추천수 높아 가져오긴 했지만, 저 풀이는 지수형태인 \"1e22\"를 넣으면 true를 반환하기 때문에<br>\n틀렸었다.. 그래서 정규식 제외한 내 풀이는 만족한다..</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><subtitle>reference</subtitle></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko\">https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30\">http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>","coverImage":"/assets/blog/cover/algorithm.jpg"}},"__N_SSG":true}